sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client/Studio
    participant Net as Module I: Network Interface
    participant Core as System Orchestrator
    
    Client->>Net: 1. Gửi Header [RequestID + PayloadLen]
    Net->>Net: Verify Magic Number & Checksum
    Client->>Net: 2. Gửi Payload [Encoded KBQL/Binary]
    Net->>Core: 3. Giải gói và Điều phối thực thi
    Core-->>Net: 4. Trả về Metadata & Row Bins
    Net-->>Client: 5. Gửi Response Frames [Result Sets]
    Net-->>Client: 6. Gửi Frame FETCH_DONE
